tools.description:
Generate audio from a structured script with multiple voices and actors. 
                    Accepts either:
                    1. Plain text string
                    2. JSON string with format: {
                        "script": [
                            {
                                "text": "Text to speak",
                                "voice_id": "optional-voice-id",
                                "actor": "optional-actor-name"
                            },
                            ...
                        ]
                    }
